{"tid":2254380,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"《環球時報》借奧斯爾抨擊黃之鋒","createTime":"2020-10-22T19:00:55.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-22T19:07:49.000Z","uid":240362,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"c9f559cc86a520c55ba6eb48ec0669083c733b97","tid":2254380,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-22T19:00:56.000Z","msg":"【綜合中國外電】奧斯爾批評被效力球會阿仙奴因政治因素被禁止上陣，事件繼續發酵。中國官媒《環球時報》昨發文抨擊奧斯爾，借「阿仙奴球迷」指該名坐擁35萬鎊（約350萬港元）周薪的德國中場，是因「不務正業」才被貶，再順勢抨擊前香港眾志秘書長黃之鋒，借題發揮。<br />\n<br />\n黃之鋒在其個人社交網上就奧斯爾言論發表意見：「我對於阿仙奴球會將奧斯爾剔出英超聯賽大軍名單的決定感到失望，原因是他曾為維吾爾族人發聲，數以百計的維人現時被困在新疆集中營。球會將為公義發聲的球員打壓，實在是難以置信，令人驚訝這球會是否正向北京（政府）磕頭。」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/sports/20201023/5XR5JWR6JJA2VEMRKTCASJUFXU/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fsports%2F20201023%2F5XR5JWR6JJA2VEMRKTCASJUFXU%2F&d=LL0CSI02xgrrxVkOh%2Fu%2FRITtxWFByFwd8BqLGIwhgUE%3D&h=e2c0f443\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fsports%2F20201023%2F5XR5JWR6JJA2VEMRKTCASJUFXU%2F&h=f4b37a29\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/sports/20201023/5XR5JWR6JJA2VEMRKTCASJUFXU/</a>"},{"pid":"72ccf8b9576ea848647a0522f5686360c165f48a","tid":2254380,"uid":305767,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-22T19:07:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />哦"}]}